@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
title Architecture technique — EduTutor IA

package "Client Browser" {
  [React + Vite\n:3000] as FRONT
}

package "Docker Compose — Serveur" {

  package "Backend" {
    [Django REST Framework\n:8000 (Gunicorn)] as API
    [PostgreSQL 15\n:5432] as DB
  }

  package "IA Layer" {
    [Ollama\nLlama 3.1 8B\n:11434] as OLLAMA
    [RAG Service\n(PyPDF2 + chunking\n+ prompt builder)] as RAG
  }

  [Nginx (reverse proxy)\n:80 / :443] as NGINX
}

FRONT --> NGINX : HTTPS
NGINX --> FRONT : / (static build)
NGINX --> API : /api/*
API --> DB : ORM Django (TCP 5432)
API --> RAG : texte source extrait
RAG --> OLLAMA : POST /api/generate\n{model, prompt}
OLLAMA --> RAG : stream JSON\n10 QCM
RAG --> API : questions[] validees (Pydantic)

note right of OLLAMA
  Modele local uniquement
  Aucune donnee externalisee
  Conformite RGPD garantie
end note

note bottom of DB
  Volume Docker persistant
  Backup quotidien recommande
end note

@enduml